54bae5f9a405a734900ceb71f01fa448e2b29d4","tid":871440,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7fbeeba4f1e02ee94d5610f1b107112f75ecd41","tid":871440,"uid":90301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"cctvb仲有播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa%2F&d=%2B2ToEs93tEd13KwEjqwzm8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b8dcf86c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5bcb18f3e60383365be49cfa/</a><br />\n2018-10-20 <br />\n有解放軍官兵處理手榴彈期間發生爆炸 當場昏迷　<br />\n<br />\n解放軍官兵近日在中越邊境雲南段，展開掃雷行動。有官兵處理一枚手榴彈期間發生爆炸，當場昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n由央視網的片段見到，官兵手牽手築成人鏈，唱著軍歌執行任務，期間一名處理一枚遺留的手榴彈時，手榴彈突然爆炸，身穿保護衣的官兵全身多處受傷，傷勢嚴重，當場昏迷，先送到附近縣醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n部隊醫院之後抽調包括外科、骨科、眼科及燒傷科等專家，組成搶救小組為他緊急治療，目前已脫離生命危險。"},{"pid":"b3c442862c6fdf00b4d8c12a8debdf242ea3d8d4","tid":871440,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"cctv自己條片刪撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://military.cctv.com/2018/10/20/ARTI1yuSG5WbhBMCGiNvDD3h181020.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmilitary.cctv.com%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2FARTI1yuSG5WbhBMCGiNvDD3h181020.shtml&d=%2B2ToEs93tEd13KwEjqwzm8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=bffa133a\" target=\"_blank\">http://military.cctv.com/2018/10/20/ARTI1yuSG5WbhBMCGiNvDD3h181020.shtml</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/chinanewscctv/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fchinanewscctv%2Fvideos&d=%2B2ToEs93tEd13KwEjqwzm8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=28a17243\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/chinanewscctv/videos</a>"},